description: This is a fun, educational fact skill aimed to teach the user random scientific facts about the planet Uranus.  These facts are taken from NASA.gov and Space.com  I hope you enjoy using Mission Uranus as much as you have had using Mission Neptune.
exampleInteractions: Alexa Ask Mission Uranus for a fact
name: Mission Uranus
shortDescription: This is a fun, educational fact skill aimed to teach the user random scientific facts about the planet Uranus. Check out Mission Neptune for ice planet news.
